Precision Demolition

show contact info 
show contact info 




Precision Demolition, based out of Abbotsford BC, is a demolition company formed in 2014 whose primary focus is pre construction demolition in residential and small commercial businesses. If you are beginning a renovation or upgrade to your home or business, or a residential house demolition give Precision Demolition a call to have your site prepped for your incoming construction crew. 

We offer professional customer service that includes post demolition clean up and have the ability to offer you material removal from your site if a bin is not provided.

Let us do the dirty work. Call or email today!
